BEGIN_TEXT
Write the given exponential function in the form \(ab^t\) and identify the initial value and the growth factor.
$BR
$BR
\( Q = $a1 \cdot $d1^{t-$f1} \) has:
$BR
$BR
\( a = \) \{ ans_rule(20) \}
\{ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") \}
$BR
\( b = \) \{ ans_rule(20) \}
\{ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") \}
END_TEXT

